<channel|>Here is a list of locations from original Vanilla World of Warcraft (Classic) lore for every letter of the alphabet:

**A** for Azeroth
**B** for Barrens
**C** for Crimson Peril (The Crimson Peril camp in Duskwood)
**D** for Dun Morogh
**E** for Eastern Kingdoms
**F** for Felwood
**G** for Gnomeregan
**H** for Hyjal (Mount Hyjal)
**I** for Ironforge
**J** for Jojo (The Jojo's area in Tanaris/Badlands)
**K** for Karazhan
**L** for Loch Modan
**M** for Mulgore
**N** for Nethergarde Keep
**O** for Orgrimmar
**P** for Ratchet
**Q** for Quagmirran (The Quagmirran area in Stranglethorn Vale)
**R** for Redridge Mountains
**S** for Stormwind
**T** for Tanaris
**U** for Undercity
**V** for Valley of Trials
**W** for Westfall
**X** for Xavius’s domain (Temple of Atiesh)
**Y** for Yell'ow (The Yell'ow area/NPCs in Desolace)
**Z** for Zul'Gurub [end of text]


